data.description: Move-In Ready High Desert Retreat for immediate enjoyment of everything the beautiful community of Meadview has to offer on a secondary or full time living basis.  Within walking distance to the downtown district, this property is perfect for Weekend Warriors, Snow Birds and Primary Residents....or even a great investment opportunity for rentals.  Extended Covered Patios afford incredible views of the Grand Wash Cliffs and West Rim of the Grand Canyon through a lens of mature Pine Trees.  Open Split Floor Plan 3Bed/2Bath Home offers privacy and intamacy.  Island Kitchen is cheerfully showcased with overhead Skylight and lined with wall to wall cabinetry.  All Appliances stay as shown.  New Metal Roof, New Vinyl Flooring and New Dual Pane Windows add to the great value.  One attached Shed with lots of Shelving and 2 Portable Bonus Utility Sheds.  Tall Car/Boat Port for Toys.  Near Launch Ramp to Lake Mead for exceptional boating, fishing and recreational opportunities.  ATV and Hiking Trails throughout the area.  Clubhouse Available with Pool, Tennis, Miniature Golf and more.  Shops, Restaurants and amenities close by.  Do not miss out on this one!
